2025-12-26 21:10:39,774 - debug_history - INFO - Generate history request body: {'messages': [{'id': '1766776138889', 'role': 'user', 'content': 'I want a 30-day reset across money, health, and time. Keep it practical. Add goals for each and track progress weekly.'}, {'id': 'efaeaec7-e4da-4cbb-9b97-109ceb46d640', 'role': 'assistant', 'content': '{"type": "viv_advice", "text": "This is an excellent decision. A simultaneous reset ensures balance, preventing one area from undermining the others. Your current Vitals are 50 across the board, which is a perfect baseline for building new systems.\\n\\nTo achieve this 30-day reset, we must immediately invest effort (Time Index reduction) to establish three critical, practical routines. We will focus on establishing small, non-negotiable habits, tracked weekly, to drive your Vitals above 60 by Day 30.\\n\\nNote: The initial drop in your Time Index reflects the focused effort required to set up these new tracking systems and daily routines. This upfront investment is crucial for long-term optimization.", "data": {"summary": "Initiating the 30-Day Triad Reset: Building Foundation.", "message_body": "This is an excellent decision. A simultaneous reset ensures balance, preventing one area from undermining the others. Your current Vitals are 50 across the board, which is a perfect baseline for building new systems.\\n\\nTo achieve this 30-day reset, we must immediately invest effort (Time Index reduction) to establish three critical, practical routines. We will focus on establishing small, non-negotiable habits, tracked weekly, to drive your Vitals above 60 by Day 30.\\n\\nNote: The initial drop in your Time Index reflects the focused effort required to set up these new tracking systems and daily routines. This upfront investment is crucial for long-term optimization.", "viv_indexes": {"financial": {"current": 50, "delta": 0, "trend": "stable"}, "health": {"current": 50, "delta": 0, "trend": "stable"}, "time": {"current": 50, "delta": -5, "trend": "down"}}, "goal_impact_analysis": "We are establishing three foundational, measurable Life Goals for the next 30 days. Successfully implementing these habits will stabilize your trajectory and immediately improve all Vitals.\\n\\nNew Targets Established:\\n1. Financial: Achieve a positive cash flow margin of 10% (Index Target: 60+).\\n2. Health: Achieve 20 days of intentional movement (Index Target: 60+).\\n3. Time: Establish and adhere to a \'Deep Work Anchor\' 5 days a week (Index Target: 60+).", "suggested_actions": ["Financial (The \'Zero-Based Check-in\'): Implement a mandatory 5-minute daily review of bank balance and spending. Set up an automated savings transfer ($5 minimum) to a separate account starting tomorrow.", "Health (The \'5-Minute Barrier Breaker\'): Commit to 5 minutes of non-negotiable physical activity (e.g., jumping jacks, planks) immediately upon waking. Fix your bedtime and set a \'Wind-Down\' alarm 45 minutes prior.", "Time (The \'Deep Work Anchor\'): Block the first 90 minutes of your workday for the single most important task (MIT), eliminating notifications and meetings during this window. Track adherence daily.", "Weekly Review: Schedule a 30-minute block every Sunday to review adherence to these three habits and calculate index progress."]}}'}, {'id': '1766776239575', 'role': 'user', 'content': 'What do you need from me to make this real, not generic?', 'date': '2025-12-26T19:10:39.575Z'}], 'context': {'location': {'lat': 29.9935803, 'lng': 31.0633813}}, 'conversation_id': 'e46ce5ec-0370-481b-8ff3-f80fde0323a2'}
