2025-12-26 21:55:02,833 - debug_history - INFO - Generate history request body: {'messages': [{'id': '1766778834742', 'role': 'user', 'content': 'Based on my affordability and last 30 days spending, can I afford a used car installment? Keep it simple and show the trade-off.'}, {'id': 'd6ec0612-7152-4a23-8c9e-ad11e1ae6f44', 'role': 'assistant', 'content': '{"type": "text", "text": "Based on your financial profile, a **safe monthly car budget is ~750 AED**.\\n*(Includes loan, insurance, fuel, and maintenance buffer)*\\n\\n**Recommended Options:**\\n- **Used Toyota Yaris (2019)**\\n  - Price: 35,000 - 45,000 AED\\n  - Monthly All-in: ~900 - 1,100 AED\\n  - *Why: Most affordable, extremely low maintenance.*\\n\\n**Next Steps:**\\n1. **Refine**: Cash or Installments?\\n2. **Save to Plan**: Track this goal.\\n3. **Connect**: Link a dealer for real inventory."}'}, {'id': '1766778902480', 'role': 'user', 'content': 'What monthly payment would you cap me at and why?', 'date': '2025-12-26T19:55:02.480Z'}], 'context': {'location': {'lat': 29.98272, 'lng': 31.0673408}}, 'conversation_id': '888e5e98-79ad-4c53-8571-a79acd721ab6'}
